Description:
WELL KEPT WATERGATE RESIDENCE WITH UPGRADED TIMBER FLOORING
A fantastic opportunity to secure this recently renovated and stylish 2 bedroom 1 bathroom apartment in the award winning Watergate Complex.
With a desirable location unmatched and packed with features and facilities, this spacious 2 bedroom will be at the top of your list.
Apartment 1004 at 8 at Waterview Walk is positioned on the 10th floor and facing the CBD. This recently upgrade 2 bedroom residence has plenty to offer:
- Large & spacious main bedroom with floor to ceiling windows, small study nook and complete with built in mirrored wardrobes.
- Additional 2nd bedroom with floor to ceiling windows facing CBD.
- Generous open plan living and dining area and direct access to a stretched balcony with dual access from master bedroom and living area.
- Recently upgraded timber flooring through out living, dining and bedrooms.
- White polish finished kitchen with plenty of cupboard storage including island bench/breakfast bar and large fridge space, SMEG stainless steel appliances including 4 burner gas cook top, range hood & dishwasher.
- Spacious bathroom with European laundry access
- Heating & Cooling.
- Secure intercom/video access.
- Secure basement parking
5 Star Facilities/Additional Features:
- Access to a very well equipped gym.
- Access to a heated pool with spa.
- Access to Sauna.
- Access to Entertainment area for guests and private functions.
Public Transport & Location:
- Free City Circle Tram at your door step.
- Short stroll to Melbourne CBD & Crown Casino.
- Within 5 minutes walk to Southern Cross Train Station & Etihad Stadium.
- Watergate is positioned between Collins St, Harbour Esp and Latrobe St tram stops.
- Walking distance to South Warf DFO.
- Close to Harbour Town Shopping Centre.
- Plenty of green parklands nearby and access to a public basketball court at the front of the building.
Property is currently leased at $510 per week unfurnished making this also a very secure and sound investment.
With a rare and unique floor plan, access to 5 star facilities and positioned in a great location, this 2 bedroom apartment at Watergate Towers should be at the top of your shopping list.

Description:
Blissful City Living with Superb North Facing View
Offering bright, stylish and relaxed modern Docklands living, this 2 bedroom apartment enjoys wonderful natural light through the floor to ceiling North facing windows.
Both bedrooms with BIRs are positioned away from each other allowing for private sleeping quarters. Spacious open plan dining and living area offers floor to ceiling windows with large balcony; bright kitchen with stone bench tops, stainless steel appliances, gas hot plates, electric oven and dishwasher with great storage. The bathroom is beautifully appointed with large separate shower, vanity and mirrors together with plenty of storage. There is an European laundry with built in shelves. communal facilities including library lounge, media room, and gymnasium
Close to Harbour Town Shopping Centre, Etihad Stadium, CBD cafes and restaurants, and Southern Cross Station.

Description:
Position, Proportion And Sleek Style
The lifestyle that you will experience while residing on the 7th floor of one of New Quay's most keenly sought after complexes, The Arkley is second to none. A sea of lights extending to the horizon, Melbourne's Star Observation Wheel and the shimmering Marina create a fairytale-like background to the beautifully bright 2-bedroom, 1-bathroom apartment's interior.
A balcony flowing off the living and dining room expands the space for relaxing and entertaining outdoors. Open-planned to the living room is a chic kitchen. Each of the bedrooms is fitted with built-in robes while a second balcony leads off the main bedroom. A powder room sits opposite the bathroom, which is appointed with a bath and separate shower. Completing the features are 2 car spaces and a European laundry.
Leisure facilities include a pool, golf net, function room and gym. The location is like no other with transport and dining-out venues at the door and the CBD within walking distance.
Please contact Charles Finnigan on 0437 204 556 to arrange an exclusive viewing

Description:
FANTASTIC VIEWS IN LARGE LACROSSE APARTMENT
Delivering spectacular city views is this large Lacrosse apartment on La Trobe Street. Comprising of 2 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, and 1 car space, this Docklands dwelling possesses space and elegance, as well as floor to ceiling windows that present a stunning vista to the north of Melbourne all the way to the CBD.
The generous open plan living area comes with a stylish kitchen complete with dishwasher, stainless steel appliances, concealed fridge, and stone bench-top. The large master bedroom comes with built-in-robes, and a chic, modern en-suite. The second bedroom is also generous in size, and includes plenty of storage with its built in robes. Both bedrooms have loads of natural light. The central bathroom completes this fab package with its clean, contemporary finishes, ample storage, and euro-laundry. A feature through-out this inner city pad is loads of storage, and is rounded out by central heating/cooling, secure swipe and intercom entry.
Typical of modern apartment living, additional facilities for residents include a fully equipped gym and heated outdoor pool. With public transport, world class shopping, and an array of waterside restaurants and bars on your doorstep, this must see apartment is perfectly situated only minutes from the CBD and CityLink.

Description:
Brand New Apartment with Water View in Docklands
Located in the heart of NewQuay, with a promise to deliver sophisticated modern character, stunning quality, and a convenient waterside location, this one bedroom apartment in the SOLD OUT building is a rare opportunity!
This building has the potential to become an iconic building for NewQuay, Docklands and Melbourne. Available to both local and offshore purchasers, opportunity to take advantage of huge stamp duty savings may be applicable.
Positioned on the 20th level, this superb apartment encompasses a stylishly contemporary interior and floor-to-ceiling windows allowing for great natural light.
Additional features include:
- Quality Miele appliances,
- Open plan living and dining area,
- Views facing the Bolte Bridge and the bay.
Luxurious resort style amenities include:
- Swimming pool on level 7,
- Cinema,
- Library,
- Private meeting rooms,
- Hotel restaurant, cafe and retail on the ground floor.
This freehold development integrates a 7-storey hotel with a total of 269 rooms and two residential towers (43 and 36 levels high), comprising of 471 apartments. The hotel will be managed by the Starwood Hotels and Resorts Worldwide (which own Sheraton, W Hotels, St Regis, to name a few) under the name Four Points By Sheraton Melbourne Docklands Hotel.
Ideal to invest or owner-occupy and situated only moments from public transport and various shopping and dining options, this location is second-to-none.
Estimated completion is Nov 2017.

Description:
Motivated Seller
Splashed with colourful, funky interiors and touches of sophistication, this one bedroom residence in the Silver Tower of the excellent Aqui Promenade will catch the attention of passionate Docklands dwellers, savvy investors and first home buyers.
Distinct timber flooring and an inimitable red and white colour scheme adds true uniqueness to this stylish abode. The open living and meals zone is low-maintenance and relaxed with direct access to a balcony which is the perfect area to partake in alfresco dinners and weekend drinks when the weather heats up.
Chic black tapware, a stone benchtop and stainless steel appliances define the fantastic kitchen, while a sizeable bedroom with BIR is steps from the immaculate and well thought out bathroom. Other property features include a European laundry, reverse cycle heating and cooling, secure intercom and access to indoor 25m swimming pool, spa, sauna, gymnasium, and lobby with private meeting rooms.
Enjoy a central NewQuay precinct position right opposite Harbour Town Shopping Centre which has a number of retail shops and casual places to dine. You’re also close to the Melbourne Star Observation Wheel, Costco, Moonee Ponds Creek Trail, Ron Barassi Snr Park, IGA supermarket and local trams.
Investors take note, with a conservative rental appraisal of $410 per week, this property will gross 5.29% if purchased for $404,000.
Please contact Thomas Tregonning on 0413 317 304 to arrange an exclusive viewing.

Description:
GREAT VIEWS FROM ICONIC 888 COLLINS
Perched neatly above Victoria Harbour and with an additional aspect along the Yarra, apartment 2211 offers one of the better vistas from the stylish 888 Collins building.
Just a few steps from the tram stop in the Free Tram Zone and with all the facilities of Victoria Harbour Precinct so close by, inspection is a must. Stroll along the Australian Wharf boardwalk to enjoy the Yarra River, marinas, South Wharf and through to Southbank. Explore Victoria Harbour and the many cafes and restaurants lining the route. Supermarkets, medical centre, The Dock Library, chemists and service businesses are all in easy walking reach.
The open plan living takes advantage of the range of views and opens on to a wide north facing balcony. The two roomy bedrooms are set apart for privacy with the master featuring ensuite bathroom. The L-shaped kitchen provides ample cupboard and bench space. Reverse cycle air-conditioning, carpark and secure entry. Inspect now.

Description:
Prime Bourke Street Living in Victoria Harbour
Promising a smart and open layout, sleek designer charm and a location just moments to relaxed cafes and restaurants on Bourke Street, this two bedroom apartment right on the city’s edge is a Docklands beauty in the terrific Serrata complex.
Step inside and be impressed by the generous space of the airy lounge and dining zone, which opens out to the immense balcony which runs across the entire apartment and provides amazing space to enjoy alfresco dining and entertaining during summer.
The stone kitchen with tiles underfoot is incorporated into the living zone and features a vibrant splashback and stainless steel European appliances. Both bedrooms come with mirrored built-in robes, while also benefit from the designer bathroom with concealed laundry, wall heating and a secure intercom entry.
The superb Victoria Harbour precinct has the advantage of being so close to the CBD while also enjoying brilliant surrounding attractions. Eateries such as Squires Loft, Banoi Docklands, Pok Pok and Taberu-Ya are right at your door, while you’re also near Docklands Park, a community garden right at the building’s rear, The Hub @ Docklands, Etihad Stadium, Woolworths supermarket and trams on up Collins Street.
Please contact Thomas Tregonning on 0413 317 304 to arrange an exclusive viewing.

Feel right at home in one of the Docklands best buildings as you enjoy the modern style and brilliant views that accompany this two bedroom apartment. Situated just a stone’s throw to Docklands Park while also being within easy reach of superb restaurants and Etihad Stadium, this smart, stylish and sizeable two bedroom apartment is a great opportunity for all buyers.
Local professionals, savvy investors and anyone wanting to live the stellar Docklands lifestyle will be impressed with this 7th floor apartment. The dual access bathroom with laundry fits in with the stylish theme of the rest of the apartment, while other extras include a charmed balcony for outdoor versatility (accessed via central living and main bedroom), central heating and cooling, intercom entry, secure car space and access to facilities including an onsite pool, sauna and gym.

Description:
Breathtaking 29th Floor City and River Views
An absolutely breathtaking Docklands opportunity is right in front of you with this brand new 3 bedroom + study, 2 bathroom apartment, which has an amazing 29th floor position in the new and exciting Forge complex.
This sky high residence truly needs to be seen to be believed, with a wonderful amount of space measuring 155 sqm (approx.) total, matched by high end fittings and fixtures and dashes of sophisticated style. The awe-inspiring city and Yarra River views have many vantage points, with the light-filled and generous winter garden featuring louvre windows the pick of the spots to soak in the vistas.
There is a wealth of space throughout the lounge and dining zone, which includes the large state of the art kitchen featuring an island bench, plenty of storage, and stainless steel appliances. All bedrooms have built-in robes including the master retreat which also enjoys a double vanity ensuite. A dedicated study and striking bathroom are other main highlights.
Additional extras include a separate laundry, ducted heating and cooling, secure intercom, storage cage, and 2 secure car spaces. Residents also have access to the Wharf’s Club with gym, pool and café as well as a private kitchen/dining room and cinema.
You’re only a brisk walk to Walk to South Wharf promenade which has eateries and bars including Plus 5 Bar, Munich Brauhaus, Citizen Café and Bar, and Common Man. Also close to DFO shops, Victoria Harbour precinct, Crown Casino with world class restaurants and entertainment, Port Melbourne and South Melbourne attractions, and Southern Cross Station.

AUCTION – 9th December 11AM
Impressing with a fantastic size for a one bedroom apartment with a large 55sqm (approx.) total size and further appealing with superb light and a low maintenance edge, this property in The Quays residential complex will have widespread appeal.
This 23rd floor gem is sure to come on the radar of city professionals with its proximity to the CBD, first home buyers and smart investors who will enjoy terrific returns. The complex is also one of the most desired in the Docklands and offers up facilities including a Health Club featuring a swimming pool, spa, sauna, gymnasium and a yoga studio. There is a Resident’s Club on Level One with a library, reading room, business centre, boardroom, private dining room & cinema lounge, while there is also a rooftop garden with BBQ, dining facilities and the only tennis court in Docklands.
You’ll love the relaxed internal living spaces including the comfortable lounge and meals zone which offers floor-to-ceiling windows and is adjoined by a stone-featured kitchen. The covered balcony (accessed via central living and bedroom) takes advantage of its position to offer breathtaking city views, while the bedroom also has CBD vistas as well as built-in robe storage.
The surrounding NewQuay precinct offers an assortment of amazing restaurants including Bopha Devi and Newquay International Buffet, while you’re also close to Harbour Town Shopping Centre, Costco, Medibank Icehouse, Melbourne Star Observation Wheel and Festival Hall. You also have access to the 70 tram which takes you through the CBD, MCG, Richmond, Hawthorn and Box Hill.

Description:
BRIGHT AND SUNNY DESIGNER LIVING IN THE HEART OF VICTORIA HARBOUR!
This spacious two bedroom apartment in the lovely Serrata Apartments building, right in the heart of Victoria Harbour, Docklands, is conveniently situated on the 3rd floor and features a large wrap around balcony with plenty of natural light and an abundance of residential friendly mod cons.
Serrata is a unique residential building situated between Bourke Street and Victoria Green. In the middle of it all, these sleek apartments represent a new era of city living: at the intersection of commerce, retail, and cultural offerings.
Key Information
•15 levels of mixed residential and commercial use
•144 apartments
Serrata comprises of 144 one and two-bedroom apartments – contemporary sanctuaries far from the hustle and bustle.
Its bold design and statement finishes are underpinned by intelligence and consideration, resulting in a space as striking as it is eco friendly.
Each apartment’s generous open-plan format allows for a sense of space not commonly associated with cosmopolitan living; finished with floor-to-ceiling windows and wide balconies these havens are flooded with natural light and offer captivating views of the city skyline.
Serrata has achieved a 4 Star Green Star Multi-Unit Residential Design rating. Each apartment is designed to furnish with ease and has a myriad of savvy green ideas to keep your carbon footprint down. Smart thinking that ensures energy efficiency.
Serrata surprises with a number of apartments that truly break the mould – some with stunning views of the city skyline, others with walk-up access from the street, and a unique loft-style residence built over two levels.
Walking distance to Etihad Stadium, Waterfront City, Southern Cross Station and close to restaurants, shopping centres, train station and tram stops.
Serrata Apartments, located in Victor Harbour, Docklands, is an edgy, design focused apartment development only moments from Collins Street and Melbourne’s CBD. The 15 level residential building with 144 apartments has been recognised with two architecture awards and the highest green star rating from the Green Building Council of Australia.
The building incorporates a range of sustainable features including the installation of smart meters in all apartments, low-e glazing double glazed windows to reduce the use of heaters & air conditioners , and a rain water tank is used for garden irrigation and toilet flushing.
Amongst the sustainability features are Safetyline Jalousie Louvre Windows which are installed in the corridors to achieve maximum cross-flow ventilation.
The louvre windows are automated and integrated with the Building Management System and feature rain sensors that automatically close the louvres in rain and then open again when weather conditions improve.
The ventilation reduces energy consumption and operating costs whilst providing fresh air and natural light to the corridors.
From a design and practical perspective, the windows appear in a continuous unit up the side of the building, meeting all balustrade codes, adding aesthetic appeal and safety to the overall development.
• 75 sqm (approx.) internal + 18 sqm (approx.) balcony = 93 sqm (approx.)
• Spacious living area
• Two large double bedrooms filled with natural light and built in robes
• A full length 18sqm balcony providing ample outdoor living area and entrainment area.
• Low owner corporation fees
Currently leased with vacant possession available.
INSPECT AS ADVERTISED OR CONTACT AGENT FOR FURTHER DETAILS.
Contact SUNNY LU on 0422 060 234 / 0434 183 780.
